OL,3,CHealth Minister confirms intention to
OL,4,Cintroduce 'duty of candour' legislation
OL,6,FStormont Health Minister Mike Nesbitt
OL,7,Fhas announced a new framework aimed at
OL,8,Fpromoting open communication between
OL,9,Fpatients, families and staff.
OL,11,FHe said the Being Open Framework comes
OL,12,Fafter several public inquiries over
OL,13,Frecent decades highlighted systemic
OL,14,Ffailings within health and social
OL,15,Fcare, particularly around openness,
OL,16,Ftransparency and accountability.
