OL,3,CHealth Minister confirms intention to
OL,4,Cintroduce 'duty of candour' legislation
OL,6,FIn a statement to the Assembly, Mr
OL,7,FNesbitt said these inquiries
OL,8,F"consistently recommended fostering a
OL,9,Fculture of openness and candour to
OL,10,Fimprove patient safety and to help
OL,11,Frebuild public confidence".
OL,13,FHe said a public consultation heard
OL,14,F"overwhelming support" for the
OL,15,Fframework.
OL,17,FImplementation is set to start in
OL,18,FApril.
