OL,3,CHealth Minister confirms intention to
OL,4,Cintroduce 'duty of candour' legislation
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt also said most consultation
OL,7,Fresponses backed the introduction of a
OL,8,Fstatutory duty of candour.
OL,10,FHe said his department is "progressing
OL,11,Ftwo important strands of work in this
OL,12,Farea", and seeking to "align Northern
OL,13,FIreland with the other UK nations in
OL,14,Frelation to both an organisational and
OL,15,Fan individual duty of candour".
