OL,3,CHealth Minister confirms intention to
OL,4,Cintroduce 'duty of candour' legislation
OL,6,FMr Nesbitt said: "Embedding an open
OL,7,Fand just learning culture is essential
OL,8,Fto help rebuild and restore public
OL,9,Fconfidence and trust, and to improve
OL,10,Fpatient safety, quality of care, and
OL,11,Fstaff wellbeing.
OL,13,F"All of the policy commitments in this
OL,14,Fpackage need to be seen in the context
OL,15,Fof learning and thereby reducing the
OL,16,Flikelihood of any recurrence of the
OL,17,Fquality failings.
