OL,3,CHealth Minister confirms intention to
OL,4,Cintroduce 'duty of candour' legislation
OL,6,F"It is clear that cultural change is a
OL,7,Fjourney and cannot be achieved
OL,8,Fimmediately ` it demands sustained
OL,9,Fcommitment, ownership, and leadership
OL,10,Fat local organisational level, and
OL,11,Fwith strong continued support from the
OL,12,Fdepartment.
OL,14,F"My department and HSC organisations
OL,15,Fremain fully committed to this
OL,16,Fjourney, ensuring that openness,
OL,17,Ftransparency, and learning become
OL,18,Fhallmarks of our health and social
OL,19,Fcare system."
